        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/alexcrichton\">alexcrichton</a> added the wasm-proposal:stack-switching label to <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13703\">Issue #13703</a>.</p>",
